This is the ONLY live recorded concert of Barry White ever made.

The legendary king of vocal seduction, Barry White is captured in this 1975 video recorded live in Frankfurt, Germany. White wraps his silken voice around such classics as "Can&#039;t Get Enough of Your Love, Babe," "I Belong to You" (Love Unlimited) and "Rhapsody in White." The Grammy Award-winning superstar hit his stride in the 1970s and is best remembered for his unique vocal style and refined performance approach to traditional R&B.
